'''hi5'''是一座总部位于美国[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[旧金山|旧金山]]的[[社交網路服務|社交網路服務]]，于2003年成立、2004年推出正式服务。[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]]曾预言称到2007年hi5将成为全球第二大社交网络，仅次于[[Myspace|Myspace]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://techcrunch.com/2007/01/20/hi5-traffic-surges-may-be-second-largest-social-network/|title=Hi5 Traffic Surges, May Be The Largest Social Network|accessdate=28 May 2015|author=Michael Arrington|work=TechCrunch|publisher=AOL|archive-date=2016-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160428212907/http://techcrunch.com/2007/01/20/hi5-traffic-surges-may-be-second-largest-social-network/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2008年，{{tsl|en|comScore||comScore}}报道称hi5是世界上最流行的社交网站之一（第3名），仅次于[[Facebook|Facebook]]和MySpace。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.comscore.com/press/release.asp?press=2396 |title=Social Networking Explodes Worldwide as Sites Increase their Focus on Cultural Relevance |postscript= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090204212650/http://www.comscore.com/press/release.asp?press=2396 |archivedate=2009-02-04 |accessdate=2016-10-03 }}</ref>2011年12月，{{tsl|en|if(we)||if(we)}}（原名{{tsl|en|Tagged||Tagged}}）收购了hi5，价格不明。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2011/12/14/tagged-acquires-facebook-competitor-hi5/|title=Tagged acquires Facebook competitor Hi5|author=Raice, Shayndi|date=December 14, 2011|website=blogs.wsj.com|accessdate=2016-10-03|archive-date=2016-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161116223701/http://blogs.wsj.com/digits/2011/12/14/tagged-acquires-facebook-competitor-hi5/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://gigaom.com/2007/07/22/hi5/|title=Social Network Hi5 gets $20 million|accessdate=August 8, 2010|date=July 22, 2007|publisher=Gigaom.com|archive-date=2017-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170710224700/https://gigaom.com/2007/07/22/hi5/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
[[File:Hi5_map.svg|thumb]]
hi5于2003年由{{tsl|en|Ramu Yalamanchi|拉穆•雅拉曼奇|拉穆•雅拉曼奇}}创立。<ref name="siliconindia.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconindia.com/shownews/Ramu_Yalamanchi_founded_hi5_raises_14_Million-nid-69812-cid-100.html|title=Ramu Yalamanchi founded hi5 raises $14 Million|accessdate=28 May 2015|author=SiliconIndia|work=siliconindia|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924122031/http://www.siliconindia.com/shownews/Ramu_Yalamanchi_founded_hi5_raises_14_Million-nid-69812-cid-100.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2004年前，公司在[[天使投资者|天使投资者]]帮助下募集到了25万美元并开始盈利。

hi5的发展速度很快，到了2006年中期，它成为了全球第八大社交网络。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mashable.com/2006/07/16/hi5-another-massive-social-network/|title=hi5, Another Massive Social Network|accessdate=28 May 2015|date=16 July 2006|work=Mashable|archive-date=2016-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161128150806/http://mashable.com/2006/07/16/hi5-another-massive-social-network/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2007年，[[莫尔达维多风险投资公司|莫尔达维多风险投资公司]]向hi5发起了一连串的风险投资，总金额高达2000万美元。hi5在欧洲、拉丁美洲和亚洲占据了大量的市场份额，玛丽·米克曾经在她2007年的技术/互联网趋势报告将其世界最大的10个网站。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.slideshare.net/kleinerperkins/technology-internet-trends-oct-2007-web-20-summit |title=Technology / Internet Trends |last=Meeker |first=Mary |date=October 18, 2007 |work=Morgan Stanley Global Technology Team |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208111431/http://www.slideshare.net/kleinerperkins/technology-internet-trends-oct-2007-web-20-summit |archivedate=2015-12-08 |accessdate=2016-10-03 }}</ref>

2009年4月，比尔·斯曼被任命为公司首席执行官，与此同时，公司开始将自己重新定位为社交游戏平台并开始向游戏开发商开放。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessweek.com/technology/content/mar2010/tc20100312_481808.htm|title=Social Network Hi5 Gets Its Game On|accessdate=August 8, 2010|author=Douglas MacMillan|date=March 12, 2010|publisher=BusinessWeek|archive-date=2014-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502094422/http://www.businessweek.com/technology/content/mar2010/tc20100312_481808.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>2010年年初，hi5收购了社交游戏公司Big Six。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://techcrunch.com/2010/02/24/hi5-acquires-social-gaming-company-big-six/|title=hi5 Acquires Social Gaming Company Big Six|accessdate=August 8, 2010|date=February 24, 2010|last=Rao|first=Leena|publisher=Techcrunch.com|archive-date=2018-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180708074229/https://techcrunch.com/2010/02/24/hi5-acquires-social-gaming-company-big-six/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2010年，hi5宣布它已从莫尔达维多募集3百万张换股票据，总资金高达800万美元。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://techcrunch.com/2010/04/01/social-network-hi5-raises-23-million-in-funding/|title=Social Network hi5 Raises $3 Million In Debt From Mohr Davidow|accessdate=August 8, 2010|date=April 1, 2010|last=Rao|first=Leena|publisher=Techcrunch.com|archive-date=2017-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170419092224/https://techcrunch.com/2010/04/01/social-network-hi5-raises-23-million-in-funding/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2010年7月，hi5从Crosslink Capital募集了1400万美元。<ref name="siliconindia.com2">{{cite web|url=http://www.siliconindia.com/shownews/Ramu_Yalamanchi_founded_hi5_raises_14_Million-nid-69812-cid-100.html|title=Ramu Yalamanchi founded hi5 raises $14 Million|accessdate=28 May 2015|author=SiliconIndia|work=siliconindia|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924122031/http://www.siliconindia.com/shownews/Ramu_Yalamanchi_founded_hi5_raises_14_Million-nid-69812-cid-100.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[File:Hi5_logo_-_2015.jpg|thumb]]
2011年1月，亚历克斯·圣约翰加入并担任了hi5的总裁兼首席技术官。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://venturebeat.com/2009/11/30/hi5-recruits-a-beastly-gaming-veteran-as-its-president/|title=hi5 recruits a beastly gaming veteran as its president|accessdate=August 8, 2010|author=Dean Takahashi|date=November 30, 2009|publisher=VentureBeat|archive-date=2016-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328104751/http://venturebeat.com/2009/11/30/hi5-recruits-a-beastly-gaming-veteran-as-its-president/|dead-url=no}}</ref>据Quantcast报道，hi5的美国月度游客达到了270万，全球访客达到了46.1万。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.quantcast.com/hi5.com?country=US#traffic|title=Hi5.com Traffic and Demographic Statistics by Quantcast|accessdate=2013-06-14|author=quantcast labs real-time profile Check it Out|date=2013-06-07|publisher=Quantcast.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130531030643/https://www.quantcast.com/hi5.com?country=US#traffic|archive-date=2013-05-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2011年，软件业资深人士卡伦·理查森开始担任该公司的董事会主席。<ref>{{cite press release|title=Hi5 expands leadership team as company experiences dramatic growth|url=http://www.hi5networks.com/press/releases/0813080.html|publisher=Hi5|accessdate=June 2, 2011|archive-date=2011-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110620082720/http://hi5networks.com/press/releases/0813080.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2011年12月，hi5的资产被{{tsl|en|if(we)||if(we)}}（原名{{tsl|en|Tagged||Tagged}}）收购。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bizjournals.com/sanfrancisco/news/2011/12/14/tagged-buys-shadow-of-hi5-of-yore.html|title=Tagged buys assets of Hi5|accessdate=28 May 2015|date=14 December 2011|work=San Francisco Business Times|archive-date=2017-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170614030908/http://www.bizjournals.com/sanfrancisco/news/2011/12/14/tagged-buys-shadow-of-hi5-of-yore.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>hi5拥有属于各种流派的200多个游戏，并以每周2至3个的速度开发新游戏。

== 特性 ==
hi5有很多典型的社交功能，如朋友圈、分享照片、用户组和更新状态。2009年，hi5被重新设计，新版增加了许多游戏和娱乐功能。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.insidesocialgames.com/2009/10/13/hi5s-new-redesign-another-big-milestone-in-its-gaming-strategy/|title=hi5's New Redesign: Another Big Milestone in its Gaming Strategy|author=Eldon, Eric|date=October 13, 2009|publisher=Inside Social Games|accessdate=2016-10-03|archive-date=2011-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110605010007/http://www.insidesocialgames.com/2009/10/13/hi5s-new-redesign-another-big-milestone-in-its-gaming-strategy/|dead-url=no}}</ref>全站共有200多个各种流派的游戏，并以每周2-3个的速度开发新游戏。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.games.com/2011/04/23/hi5-gaining-momentum-among-top-online-social-gaming-sites/|title=Hi5 gaining momentum among top online/social gaming sites; should Facebook be concerned?|author=Shaul, Brandy|date=April 23, 2011|publisher=Games.com|accessdate=2016-10-03|archive-date=2012-07-07|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120707152504/http://blog.games.com/2011/04/23/hi5-gaining-momentum-among-top-online-social-gaming-sites/|dead-url=no}}</ref>有的用户会将他们的个人资料展示给所有人查看；其他用户则只展示给自己圈子里的人。如果想加入hi5，您必须年满18岁。

== 市场 ==
由于hi5的服务中心转移到了社交游戏上，ComScore在2011年年初将hi5重新划分为在线游戏网站。根据ComScore的数据，hi5是全球总流量第六多的在线游戏网站。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://venturebeat.com/2011/04/20/hi5-becomes-a-top-ten-online-game-site/|title=hi5 Becomes a Top Ten Online Game Site|author=Takahashi, Dean|date=April 20, 2010|publisher=Venturebeat.com|accessdate=2016-10-03|archive-date=2016-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161116081403/http://venturebeat.com/2011/04/20/hi5-becomes-a-top-ten-online-game-site/|dead-url=no}}</ref>尽管hi5的总部设在美国，它在其他国家更受欢迎，尤其是拉丁美洲。截至2015年4月，hi5的Alexa全球排名为第2069名。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/hi5.com|title=Alexa Site Overview|accessdate=April 28, 2015|date=|publisher=Alexa.com|archive-date=2015-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150424174532/http://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/hi5.com|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== Magi.com ==
被收购后，hi5的管理团队创立了一个纯粹的游戏网站——Magi.com，并将其开放给其他游戏开发商。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/164620/Former_Hi5_president_Alex_St_John_reveals_new_social_games_network.php|title=Gamasutra - Former Hi5 president Alex St. John reveals new social games network|accessdate=28 May 2015|author=Mike Rose|publisher=|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304050833/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/164620/Former_Hi5_president_Alex_St_John_reveals_new_social_games_network.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>2012年6月，Magi.com关闭。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.insidesocialgames.com/2012/06/06/magi-com-shutting-down/|title=Magi.com shutting down|accessdate=28 May 2015|publisher=|archive-date=2014-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140512232524/http://www.insidesocialgames.com/2012/06/06/magi-com-shutting-down/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

